    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle retains its original showroom luster, featuring a flawless exterior profile and an interior that remains in pristine, untouched condition. Mechanically uncompromising and meticulously documented, this motorcar offers a driving experience indistinguishable from new. For the collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of distinguished pedigree.",
      "price": 48500.0,
