    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total dream! This car is in truly pristine, mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it from day one and it\u2019s been garage-kept its whole life. It honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or smudge to be found! I'm looking for a new owner who will love it as much as I have. Come see it for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
