    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54B32 platform. The naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, delivering linear power through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including a full VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The rear subframe has been professionally reinforced with plates to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. Equipped with a variable M differential lock and a perfectly balanced 50:50 weight distribution, the chassis provides exceptional feedback and turn-in precision. Every mechanical component, from the cooling system to the suspension bushings, remains in peak operational status.",
